title: The Complete Hayley Smith American Dad Timeline

media:group.media:title: The Complete Hayley Smith American Dad Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire timeline of Hayley Smith from American Dad. Created by Seth MacFarlane, we look at Hayley's entire life story, her past and future. Taking a look at the full American Dad episodes, I've put Hayley's life in chronological order. From season 1 to American Dad season 19.
I talk about how she met her husband Jeff Fischer, and her relationship with her father Stan Smith. 

We also look at the funniest American Dad moments with Stan Smith, Roger, Francine, Hayley and Steve. As well as other American Dad characters from Langley Falls.

#Americandad #Timeline #Hayley #rogersmith 

Script by: Helen Armitage
